headline: How Investors Are Reacting To FactSet (FDS) Integrating AI-Powered JumpStart for Enhanced Equity Trading
summary: FactSet recently announced the integration of IntelligentCross's JumpStart functionality with its Portware execution management system, becoming the first among peers to offer direct buy-side access to Jefferies' low-touch algorithmic liquidity. This new collaboration leverages artificial intelligence to enhance equity trading, aiming to deliver improved liquidity access with minimal information leakage for institutional clients.
